Ecuadorians Blocked From Enforcing Chevron Judgment Get Expedited Appeal

-- B y   K a r e n   G u l l o
-- 
2011-05-12T20:40:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-12/ecuadorians-blocked-from-enforcing-chevron-judgment-get-expedited-appeal.html
Ecuadoreans suing  Chevron Corp. (CVX)  over
environmental damage in the Amazon won a partial stay of a U.S.
court order blocking enforcement of an Ecuador court judgment in
their favor.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Karen Gullo in San Francisco at 
 kgullo@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
